{"article_id":"fecYZ0B9tfsDsUba","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Thursday canceled the highly anticipated summit with North Korea","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that had been set for next month ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"calling the talks \" inappropriate \"","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"following the \" hostility \"","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"displayed in the latest comments from dictator Kim Jong Un .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The move","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to pull out of the summit ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"slated to take place in Singapore on June 12 ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"came after threats from Kim","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"to call off the talks .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"In a letter to Kim on Thursday , Trump said","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"the world , and North Korea , had lost a `` great opportunity for lasting peace and great prosperity . ''","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"\" Based on the tremendous anger and open hostility","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"displayed in your most recent statement ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"I feel","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"it is inappropriate , at this time , to have this long-planned meeting , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Trump wrote in a letter to Kim on Thursday .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"\" Therefore , please let this letter serve to represent","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"that the Singapore summit , for the good of both parties ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"but to the detriment of the world , will not take place . \"","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"North Korea has for days questioned","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"whether the summit would go forward .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"On Thursday , Vice Minister of the North Korean Foreign Ministry , Choe Son Hui , also said","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that whether the U.S. `` will meet us at a meeting room","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"or encounter us at nuclear-to-nuclear showdown is entirely dependent upon the decision and behavior of the United States , ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"according to South Korea 's Yonhap News Agency .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"The official also insulted Vice President Pence","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"after he said","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"North Korea had asked for the meeting .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"`` As a person","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"involved in the U.S. affairs ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"I can not suppress my surprise at such ignorant and stupid remarks","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"gushing out from the mouth of the U.S. vice president , ''","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Choe reportedly said .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Officials , though , told Fox News","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"that it was the threat of nuclear war","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"-- not the insult to Pence --","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"that led to the summit pullout .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" You talk about your nuclear capabilities ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"but ours are so massive and powerful","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"that I pray to God","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"they will never have to be used , \"","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Trump wrote to Kim .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"\" If you change your mind","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"having to do with this most important summit ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"please do not hesitate to call me","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"or write .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"The world , and North Korea in particular , has lost a great opportunity for lasting peace and great prosperity and wealth . \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Trump added ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"\" This missed opportunity is truly a sad moment in history . \"","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"The president also expressed his gratitude for the release of the three American hostages from North Korea earlier this month .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo had traveled to North Korea on a surprise diplomatic mission","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"to retrieve the American prisoners ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"and even met with Kim in preparation for the summit .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" I want to thank you for the release of the hostages","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"who are now home with their families , \"","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Trump wrote .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"\" That was a beautiful gesture","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"and was very much appreciated . \"","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"AMERICAN PRISONERS HELD IN NORTH KOREA ON THEIR WAY HOME AFTER POMPEO VISIT ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"TRUMP SAYS","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"He added ,","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"\" Some day , I look very much forward to meeting you . ''","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Pompeo ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"who had met with Kim in North Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"testified on Capitol Hill Thursday before the Senate Foreign Intelligence Committe ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"to discuss the State Department 's budget","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"as the news from the White House broke .","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"`` I can add , over past many days ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that we have endeavored to do","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"what Kim and I agreed ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"put teams togehter in advance of the summit ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"and we received no response from North Korea , ''","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"`` The American team was rocking ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"were ready , and fully prepared for this meeting . ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Pompeo added","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that there was `` little doubt ''","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that Kim understood `` the scope '' of what the U.S. was requesting .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"`` We made this abundantly clear through multiple channels , ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"`` I regreat statements","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"North Korea made over the past few days ,","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"and that we have n't been able to conduct prep","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"necessary for a successful summit . ''","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"The anticipated summit was set to come on the heels of a \" historic meeting \" between North and South Korea last month ,","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"as leaders from the two nations pledged to clear the peninsula of nuclear weapons .","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Moon and Kim announced","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"they would work","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"to achieve a \" nuclear-free Korean Peninsula , \"","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"and also expressed hope","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"to officially end the 1950-53 Korean War by the end of the year ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"though it is not clear at this point the steps","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"the leaders will take","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"to achieve denuclearization .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"\" KOREAN WAR TO END !","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"The United States , and all of its GREAT people , should be very proud of what is now taking place in Korea ! \"","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"Trump tweeted last month .","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"The leaders had agreed","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"that by May 1 , the loudspeaker propaganda broadcasts","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that had been blaring from each side of the heavily armed border","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"would be suspended .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"They agreed to also dismantle broadcasting equipment and stop flying propaganda leaflets across their border .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"Kim also promised Moon","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"that he \" won ' t interrupt \" his \" early morning sleep anymore , \"","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"referring to missile tests ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"South Korea said .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"But Kim ' s tune changed last week ,","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"canceling a high-level summit with Moon ,","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"following U.S.-South Korean military exercises ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"the state-run Korean media outlet suggested","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"were a rehearsal for a potential invasion of the North .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"During Trump 's meeting on Monday with Moon in the Oval Office , the South Korean president expressed confidence in the summit , and in `` the future of Kim . ''","depth":3},{"id":114,"text":"`` In the end , it will work out .","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"I ca n't tell you how or why ,","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"but in the end it will work out , ''","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"`` It always does . ''","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":177,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":138,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":128,"right":137,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":123,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":120,"right":122,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":2,"right":121,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":125,"right":126,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":5,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":129,"right":136,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":129,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"